 di store kami..!!
 Harap gunakan dengan bijak
 Happy surfing..!!
⚪══════════════════⚪
<code> ✦ Hostname   :</code> <code>$domain</code>
<code> ✦ Username   :</code> <code>$username</code>
<code> ✦ UUID       :</code> <code>$uuid</code>
<code> ✦ Limit IP   :</code> <code>$iplimit User</code>
<code> ✦ Limit Quota:</code> <code>$quota GB</code>
<code> ✦ Port TLS   :</code> <code>400-900</code>
<code> ✦ Port nTLS  :</code> <code>80, 8080</code>
<code> ✦ Path       :</code> <code>/Multi-Path</code>
<code> ✦ Path WS    :</code> <code>/vmess</code>
<code> ✦ Path gRPC  :</code> <code>vmess-grpc</code>
⚪══════════════════⚪
<code> ✦ Expired : $exp_date</code>
⚪══════════════════⚪
 ✦ TLS <code>${link_tls}</code>
⚪══════════════════⚪
 ✦ nTLS <code>${link_ntls}</code>
⚪══════════════════⚪
 ✦ TLS CONFERENCE <code>${link_grpc}</code>
⚪══════════════════⚪
 ✦ <code>https://${domain}:81/vmess-$username.txt</code>
⚪══════════════════⚪"

if [[ -n "$CHATID" && -n "$KEY" ]]; then
  curl -s --max-time 10 \
    -d "chat_id=$CHATID&disable_web_page_preview=1&text=$TEXT&parse_mode=html" \
    $URL >/dev/null
fi

# ==========================
# Notifikasi Transaksi (Channel)
# ==========================
BOT_TOKEN_TRX="8220003675:AAH3Kc8DpW-pklkQZ3FJ7Eei19lfUvj7ofU"
